Jack Gilford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Gilford 0 Jack Gilford (July 25, 1908 – June 4, 1990) was an American Broadway, film and television actor. He was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor for Save the Tiger (1973). Jack_Gilford ( July_25_,_1908 – June_4_,_1990 ) was an_American_Broadway_,_film_and_television_actor .
